high_descs: Go right and then right again and turn to the left to face the striped couch.
Pick the credit card up from the couch.
Move to the left and face the lamp in the counter.
Turn the lamp in the corner on.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a credit card and turn a lamp on.

high_descs: Walk forward to the door, then turn right and walk to the credit card on the sofa.
Pick up the credit card from the sofa.
Turn left and walk to the tall lamp in the corner next to the sofa.
anns.task_desc: Examine a credit card by the light of a floor lamp.

high_descs: Walk to the direction of the door, hang a right to stand in front of the left cushion of the sofa.
Pick up the red credit card from the left cushion.
Walk to the floor lamp at the left side of the sofa.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a credit card from the sofa, turn on a lamp
